<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="..\config8\suzuki.xsl" ?><!DOCTYPE suzuki [<!ENTITY % sdatacharaents SYSTEM "..\config8\sdatacharaents.txt">%sdatacharaents;]><suzuki><manual>
<section sectnbr = "5A">
<servcat sctnbr = "05" scnbr = "01">
<configtype typenbr = "0">
<servinfotype sitcode = "4">
<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AENAP70B5104011" svcinfotypenbr = "06" svcinfoqualnbr = "01" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Manual Road Test
</title>
<attention1>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Perform road test in a place where there is no traffic to prevent an accident.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Road test should be performed with two persons, a driver and a tester, on a level road.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention1>
<ptxt>
This test checks the gears being used in “L”, “2”, “D” (O/D OFF) or “D” (O/D ON) range when driven with deactivated gear shift control system. Test drive vehicle on a level road.
</ptxt>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
Before this test, check DTC.
</ptxt>
</attention3>
<s1>
<ptxt>
With select lever in “P” range, start engine and warm it up.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
After warming up engine, set ignition “OFF” and disconnect solenoid connector (1).
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70B510017.jpg" width = "88.000mm" height = "57.381mm" ver = "01" gw = "199" gh = "146"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<c-change/>
<s1>
<ptxt>
With select lever in “L” range, start vehicle and check that 3rd gear is being used referring to the following table.
</ptxt>
<spec>
<title>
Vehicle speed at 1000 rpm in engine speed
</title>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "1.212in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "2.259in"/>
<thead>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Gear position
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Vehicle speed
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
1st
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
8.1 km/h (5 mile/h)
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
2nd
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
14.5 km/h (9 mile/h)
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
3rd
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
23.2 km/h (14 mile/h)
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
4th
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
33.3 km/h (21 mile/h)
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
Reverse
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
10.1 km/h (6 mile/h)
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</spec>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
While vehicle is running, shift select lever to “2” range and check that 3rd gear is being used.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
While vehicle is running, shift select lever to “D” range and check that 3rd gear is being used.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
After the checks, stop vehicle then set ignition “OFF”, and reconnect solenoid connector.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Clear DTC. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70B5104004"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<p-change/>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70B5104011001">
<title>
Troubleshooting
</title>
<diag type = "condition" id = "AENAP70B5104011002">
<condition>
<ptxt>
Operated gear is not correct
</ptxt>
</condition>
<ps>
<ptxt>
Faulty valve body component
</ptxt>
</ps>
<action>
<ptxt>
<intxref refid = "AENAP70B5106026">Valve Body Assembly Removal and Installation</intxref>
.
</ptxt>
</action>
<ps>
<ptxt>
Faulty clutch or brake
</ptxt>
</ps>
<action>
<ptxt>
Check clutch and brake referring to 
<intxref refid = "AENAP70B5106064">A/T Assembly Reassembly</intxref>
.
</ptxt>
</action>
</diag>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
</servcat>
</section></manual></suzuki>
